                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su",
                "text": "A munavri can instantly learn how to use almost any device. Once per day, she can select one weapon, suit of armor, or spell trigger item on which she has cast <i>object reading</i>. For a number of minutes equal to her character level, she is considered proficient with that item or can make use of the spell trigger device as if she were a spellcaster of the appropriate class."
